{"tid":2268983,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★泰國電信商禁止市民瀏覽 PornHub 網站","createTime":"2020-11-03T07:46:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-03T10:13:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f874af95253ee1d779e7f45d97eaba2f9f7e5f15","tid":2268983,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:46:49.000Z","msg":"泰國電信商 True 早前禁止市民瀏覽 PornHub 網站，稱因為當中包含不適當的內容，隨後引起市民譁然，Ture 隨即表示該網站並沒有封鎖。但最近有泰國網民又發現，無法瀏覽 PornHub 網站，該網站被封鎖。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n早前 Ture 在 Twitter 上表示限制 PornHub 的訪問，是因為包含不適當的內容，隨後為了平息網民憤怒，該公司在幾小時後撤回了聲明，表示該網站實際上並未遭到封鎖。但最近有網民發現 PornHub 網站被封鎖，無法瀏覽，隨即引起網民討論，有網民表示荒謬、侵犯顧客的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/11/03/thai-block-pornhub/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F11%2F03%2Fthai-block-pornhub%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=tGWxp70K68wBh01xS7f0EmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=be45ab9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/11/03/thai-block-pornhub/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"153f77a9812d005eb49f12dd62d19560d0733383","tid":2268983,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90f7e7fad8b91f3e8702bad84302cc26c11306f","tid":2268983,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-03T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"遲d會唔會禁止市民扑嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gi